Many of you have been telling me I seem happier and that I have a glow about me recently. Honestly I am so much happier at this phase of life than I have ever been, I have always been overprotective of my peace of mind, my personal space and my heart in order to maintain a positive environment for myself but even more so now. So thank you for noticing that I am living my life unapologetically and not just existing, it has not been easy but it is worth it 🙏🏻❤️
